The paper also discusses the size of separating automata, which is a topic in computational complexity, suggesting that it could belong to the cs.CC (Computational Complexity) sub-category. The paper also mentions the idea of saturation, which is a topic in artificial intelligence and machine learning, suggesting that it could belong to the cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) sub-category.
